      • parse

        public boolean parse(java.lang.String xml)
        Method that parses downloaded XML data into values that are used to set the values of an Earthquake object. The method uses an XmlPullParserFactory that begins at a start tag name, 'item', and end tag '/item' and then searches for matching tag names that contain any data between them. This data is cleaned and formatted using StringBuilders if needed before being used to set as value of a newly created Earthquake object. This Earthquake object is then added to the earthquakes ArrayList.
        Parameters:
        xml - String containing XML data
        Returns:
        Status if parsing was completed successfully.
